Day 49: Deploy Applications with Kubernetes Deployments

Date: October 16, 2025
Overview
Learned to use Deployments for scalable application management.
Key Concepts Learned

Deployments vs Pods
Replica sets
Declarative configuration
Scaling applications

Commands Used
bashkubectl create deployment nginx --image=nginx --replicas=3
kubectl get deployments
kubectl scale deployment nginx --replicas=5
Challenges Faced
Understanding how Deployments manage ReplicaSets which manage Pods. The abstraction layers took time to grasp!
